title: [Zandactyl's Armory]
[Zandactyl's Combat Gear]
description: Blue watered silk walls rise from a mistwood plank floor.  Just above a bronzed drake sculpture hangs a ruby-eyed grinning skull, and a vaulted ceiling completes the picture.  A glass-topped mistwood counter and a gilded maple cabinet stand side by side in the middle of the room.
